                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/doraeomon0620/">杨羊羊多啦</a>
                    <span>2017-06-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">书里面有好几处重复，非常有我为了凑字数写论文写完懒得再检查一遍的既视感，然而如果这样就说这本书不好，那我大概算是犯了作者所说的“不当的或谬误的类比”以及“因人废言和动机论”这两个错误</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1170329751">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1170329751" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1170329751" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1170329751">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Yvonne-mimi222/">water_222</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-03-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这本书虽然大块头，但是很好读，2017年能看到这本书我很满足。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
